The '''Norton Asteroid Belt''' was in the [[Aquilaean system]], between [[Aquilae (The Star Wars)|Aquilae]] and the [[Forbidden Systems]].

When [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]], [[Annikin Starkiller]], [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia]], [[R2-D2/Legends|Artoo]], [[C-3PO/Legends|Threepio]], [[Biggs Darklighter/Legends|Biggs]] and [[Windy Starkiller|Windy]] (in [[microcase]]s) escaped [[Gordon]] in a stolen [[Imperial starship]], they headed into the Norton Asteroid Belt in an attempt to shake off pursuing [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[hunter destroyer]]s.

While they were able to destroy several, their starship was critically damaged and they evacuated above the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin]].

[[Norton Three]] was apparently one of the [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroids]].

==Behind the scenes==
The scenes in the asteroid belt inspired the events in the [[Hoth system/Legends|Hoth system]] belt in [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|Episode V]].

